      <description>&lt;p&gt;&#xA;I have been tracking my sleep using org-mode, to try and get a better understanding of what might affect my sleep. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;To be very honest though, while I have been doing this for a little over a year (adding more data points over time), I can&amp;#39;t say I have yet seen any pattern.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-container-headline-1&#34; class=&#34;outline-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;headline-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;Basic setup&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-text-headline-1&#34; class=&#34;outline-text-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;I have a date tree configured in a file named &lt;code&gt;diary.org&lt;/code&gt;, with the various data points in the &lt;code&gt;:PROPERTIES:&lt;/code&gt; drawer. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;The overview of which looks like this:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
